                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-8 col-sm-8 resume-right">
                        <h4>Oct'2016 - Current</h4>
                        <h3>Rakuten, Inc. Tokyo, Japan.</h3>
                        <p>I work for Rakuten Pay(R-Pay) under the Mobile Payment Section, Rakuten FinTech Service. I work at the server side of the Rakuten Pay (mobile payment application) which includes API development for the App developers for card payment using QR code & Barcode. I develop batch processes for Rpay business to generate/monitor daily payment data and GMS details.</br>
                        Apart for these developments, I take care of all the Server Operations(which includes server deployments, DB handling, SSL certificate management, API access passthroughs for using Rakuten internal services, etc.) and Infrastructure management(creating servers domains, nodes, instances, clusters, etc. and managing the test environment for continuos testing) for R-Pay.</p>
